('639059737aa83', 'Robert Smith', 'robert-smith', 'Robert Smith', '<p>The ICE Institute is a fantastic, ambitious, yet well implemented example of the transformation in Higher Education that is so going to empower Nations such as Indonesia to accelerate the development of Human Capital to empower their digital economy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Higher Education Lead Microsoft APAC</strong></p>\r\n', 'RobertSmith', 9, 11, 2, 'post', '639059737aa83.PNG', '2022-12-07 05:14:27', '2022-12-20 03:35:02', 34),
('63905a9235b56', 'Dr. Marito Garcia', 'dr-marito-garcia', 'Dr. Marito Garcia', '<p>The creation of a national online course marketplace with content from Indonesian universities, as well as from international content providers has given Indonesian students the ability to access the best online courses and knowledge relevant to the growing Indonesian economy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ADB Consultant</strong></p>\r\n', 'Dr.maritoGarcia', 9, 11, 2, 'post', '63905a9235b56.jpg', '2022-12-07 05:19:14', '2022-12-20 03:35:36', 50),
('639152aeb2a3a', 'The 18th Cyber Education Forum (CEF)', 'the-18th-cyber-education-forum-cef', 'Unit Pengembangan Pembelajaran Dalam Jaringan Indonesia (UPPDJI) atau yang dikenal dengan Indonesia Cyber Education Institute (ICE-I) mempersembahkan The 18th Cyber Education Forum (CEF) Universitas Terbuka (UT), dengan tema Online Course Development Based on the TPACK-IDLE Model for Professional Teacher\'s Programs.', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/Flyer_18th_CEF.png\" style=\"height:1080px; width:1080px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unit Pengembangan Pembelajaran Dalam Jaringan Indonesia (UPPDJI) atau yang dikenal dengan Indonesia Cyber Education Institute (ICE-I) mempersembahkan The 18th Cyber Education Forum (CEF) Universitas Terbuka (UT), dengan tema Online Course Development Based on the TPACK-IDLE Model for Professional Teacher&#39;s Programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kegiatan&nbsp;berlangsung pada Rabu, 23 November&nbsp;2022 yang&nbsp;dihadiri oleh:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Prof. Paulina Pannen, M.LS. (Head of ICE Institute)<br />\r\n2. Prof. Liz Johnson (Deputy Vice Chancellor, Academics &amp; Alfred Deakin Professor)<br />\r\n3.&nbsp;Dr. Nur Arifah Drajati, M.Pd. (Faculty of Teacher Training and Education)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moderator oleh Siti Hadianti, S.Pd., M.Pd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Berikut ini adalah materi yang dipaparkan oleh pembicara pada webinar ini:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe align=\"middle\" frameborder=\"1\" height=\"876\" scrolling=\"yes\" src=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RjQZdoZWwUijypjfvSzRWTjUtr-AL-xU/preview\" width=\"1000\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe align=\"middle\" frameborder=\"1\" height=\"876\" scrolling=\"yes\" src=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DVhLcPL2xLqk1YUvFgkDv2iKiLuVh1n8/preview\" width=\"1000\"></iframe></p>\r\n', 'cybereducationforum,webinarseries,18thCEF', 7, 10, 2, 'post', '639152aeb2a3a.