('63c7b7a593ef6', 'Daftar di ice institute tapi tidak dapat mengakses matakuliah', 'daftar-di-ice-institute-tapi-tidak-dapat-mengakses-matakuliah', 'sudah daftar di ice institute tapi tidak dapat mengakses matakuliah', '<h1>Sudah daftar di <a href=\"https://icei.ac.id/register?next=%2F\" target=\"_blank\">ice institute</a> tapi tidak dapat mengakses matakuliah...? saat diklik matakuliah yang di pilih terlihat tulisan &quot; <span style=\"background-color:#e74c3c\">Enrollment in this course is by invitation only</span>&quot; untuk mengakses matakuliah sesuai pilihan, anda diwajibkan mengikuti alur yang ditetapkan pada <a href=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/pendaftaran-beasiswa-kemendikbudristek-ice-institute-batch-4-semester-genap-2023\" target=\"_blank\">link</a>, matakuliah yang ada di galery ice institute saat ini bersifat <em>invitation only</em>, jadi akun anda harus didaftarkan terlebih dahulu, jika sudah terdaftar pada matakuliah tersebut, anda dapat langsung mengikuti perkuliahan atau lihat jadwal apakah matakuliah yang anda pilih sudah dibuka atau terjadwal.</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Enrollment in this course is by invitation only\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/12.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>saya sudah mendaftarkan diri di edx.org dan mengambil <a href=\"https://explore-catalog.edx.org/?enterprise_catalog_query_titles=Education&amp;hide_cards=true&amp;hide_price=true&amp;availability=Available%20Now&amp;availability=Upcoming&amp;content_type=course&amp;learning_type=course\" target=\"_blank\">matakuliah</a>, namun saat memulai perkuliahan diminta update atau berbayar....?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"diminta bayar di edx\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/21.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>itu disebabkan akun anda belum terdaftar di dari ice institute,silahkan lihat <a href=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/pendaftaran-beasiswa-kemendikbudristek-ice-institute-batch-4-semester-genap-2023\" target=\"_blank\">panduan</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>saya sudah melakukan pendaftaran di <a href=\"https://www.coursera.org/\" target=\"_blank\">coursera.org</a> dan mengambil matakuliah tapi masih diminta bayar...?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"coursera\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/31.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>jika anda mengalami hal diatas, silahkan lihat <a href=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/pendaftaran-beasiswa-kemendikbudristek-ice-institute-batch-4-semester-genap-2023\" target=\"_blank\">panduan </a>ice insitute.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'cara-akses,matakuliah,dimintabayar', 8, 14, 2, 'post', '63c7b7a593ef6.png', '2023-01-18 05:11:01', '2023-01-18 05:24:52', 461),
('63d0e36e02175', 'Pengumuman Beasiswa Kemendikbudristek ICE Institute Batch 4 Semester 2023_1', 'pengumuman-beasiswa-kemendikbudristek-ice-institute-batch-4-semester-2023_1', 'Pengumuman Beasiswa Mendikbudristek ICE Institute Batch 4 Semester 2023_1', '<h3 dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Halo Teman - teman ICE Institute!</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h5 dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Berdasarkan hasil verifikasi yang telah dilakukan, ICE Institute mengucapkan selamat bagi para peserta yang telah ditetapkan sebagai penerima Beasiswa Mendikbudristek Merdeka Belajar Untuk Semua ICE Institute Batch 4 semester 2023.1 pada Mata Kuliah Nasional, Internasional (edX, XuetangX, dan Coursera), dan Mata Kuliah Mikrokredensial yang dapat dilihat pada lampiran di bawah ini..</span></span></h5>\r\n\r\n<h5>&nbsp;</h5>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>Pengumuman Beasiswa Mendikbudristek ICE Institute Batch 4 semester 2023.1</strong></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><iframe height=\"480\" src=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1xwk4LyHLJ8F8jJciBWPydg6NBh6nT7-d/preview\" width=\"640\"></iframe></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h5><em><strong>Periode Data Masuk 1 Desember 2022 - 26 Februari 2023</strong></em></h5>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Untuk mendownloadnya silahkan klik link berikut:<span style=\"color:#3498db\"> </span><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1xwk4LyHLJ8F8jJciBWPydg6NBh6nT7-d/edit\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">Pengumuman MBUS Batch 4</span></a></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Bagi peserta yang telah dinyatakan sebagai penerima Beasiswa Mendikbudristek ICE Institute Batch 4 semester 2023.1, dapat mengikuti petunjuk untuk memulai perkuliahan sebagai berikut:</span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h5><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Petunjuk untuk Mata Kuliah <strong>Nasional</strong><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mknasional\"><span style=\"color:#ee1522\">link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mknasional</span></a></span></span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Petunjuk untuk Mata Kuliah <strong>Internasional (edX)</strong><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceiedx\"><span style=\"color:#ee1522\">link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceiedx</span></a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h5><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Petunjuk untuk Mata Kuliah <strong>Internasional (XuetangX)</strong><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceixuetang\"><span style=\"color:#ee1522\">https://link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceixuetang</span></a></span></span></h5>\r\n\r\n<h5><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Petunjuk untuk Mata Kuliah <strong>Internasional (Coursera)</strong><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceicoursera\"><span style=\"color:#ee1522\">link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceicoursera</span></a></span></span></h5>\r\n\r\n<h5><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Petunjuk untuk Mata Kuliah <strong>Mikrokredensial</strong><br />\r\n<a href=\"http://link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceimicroc\"><span style=\"color:#ee1522\">link.icei.ac.id/mulai-mkiceimicroc</span></a></span></span></h5>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Petunjuk memulai mata kuliah di ICE Institute juga telah kami kirimkan melalui masing -&nbsp; masing email peserta.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Para peserta dimohon untuk memastikan email yang tertera pada pengumuman sudah sesuai dengan email yang diajukan pada saat pendaftaran, dan memastikan alamat emailnya aktif.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cara memulai mempelajari mata kuliah yang teman teman pilih juga kami kirimkan kealamat email sesuai dengan daftar pengumuman.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Periode pembelajaran di mulai 13 Februari 2023 - 30 Juni 2023.</span></span></strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Setiap peserta yang sudah menyelesaikan setiap mata kuliah yang dipilih, dan telah klaim sertifikat, dapat memilih mata kuliah internasional (edX, XuetangX, dan Coursera) tambahan dengan menghubungi ICE Institute.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Demikian pengumuman ini kami sampaikan, jika ada yang perlu ditanyakan dan dikonfirmasikan, silahkan hubungi kami pada jam operasional Senin - Jumat jam 08.00 &ndash; 17.00 melalui nomor Hotline WhatsApp ICE Institute <a href=\"https://wa.me/6281250504200\"><span style=\"color:#ee1522\">(+62) 812-5050-4200.</span></a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Salam,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Merdeka Belajar Untuk Semua</span></span></p>\r\n', 'pengumuman,beasiswakemendikbudristek,iceinstitute,batch4,semester2023.1', 8, 14, 2, 'post', '63d0e36e02175.png', '2023-01-25 04:08:14', '2023-07-25 05:32:40', 4261),
('63d0f148443cb', 'The 19th Cyber Education Forum (CEF)', 'the-19th-cyber-education-forum-cef', 'Hallo Sahabat ICE Institute,  ICE Institute kembali menyelenggarakan Webinar Series Cyber Education Forum ke-19 dengan topik ', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/Flyer_CEF_19.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hallo Sahabat ICE Institute,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ICE Institute kembali menyelenggarakan Webinar Series Cyber Education Forum ke-19 dengan topik &quot;Software Development for Measuring Digital Skills&quot; yang diselenggarakan pada&nbsp;<br />\r\nHari: Selasa, 31 Januari 2023<br />\r\nJam: 09.00-11.00 WIB melalui Zoom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pendaftaran pada link <a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/daftarCEF19\"><strong>https://link.icei.ac.id/daftarCEF19</strong></a>, GRATIS!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saksikan live streaming melalui zoom: <a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/CEF19th\"><strong>https://link.icei.ac.id/CEF19th</strong></a>&nbsp;<br />\r\ndan dapat disaksikan juga pada channel YouTube UTTV <a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/StreamingCEF\"><strong>https://link.icei.ac.id/StreamingCEF</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nTerimakasih</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Salam,<br />\r\nMerdeka Belajar Untuk Semua!</p>\r\n', 'cybereducationforum,19thcef,webinarseries', 7, 10, 2, 'post', '63d0f148443cb.png', '2023-01-25 05:07:20', '2023-01-25 05:10:05', 235),
('63d9ecaa912c8', 'Guide to Getting Started on Microcredential Courses - ICE Institute', 'guide-to-getting-started-on-microcredential-courses-ice-institute', 'Guide to Getting Started on Microcredential Courses - ICE Institute', '<p><span style=\"font-size:36px\"><strong>Guide to Getting Started on Coursera Courses - ICE Institute</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1. Go to<span style=\"color:#3498db\"> </span><u><strong><a href=\"http://icei.ac.id\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#3498db\">icei.ac.id</span></a></strong></u>&nbsp;, scroll to <strong>&#39;Mitra&#39;</strong> part and look for coursera icon. Click<strong> &#39;lihat&#39;/&#39;view&#39; </strong>to go to coursera website</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/coursera1.png\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2. If you&#39;re logged in on Coursera, make sure to log out first.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3.Check your e-mail inbox. Make sure that the email address is the same as the one in announcement list.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4.Find the invitation email on your inbox. It looks like the image shown below</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/coursera2.png\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5.Click <strong>&#39;Join Now&#39;</strong> to join the Coursera Program.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/coursera3.png\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6. You will be redirected to this screen. Check whether your&nbsp;email address was registered on Coursera. If not,&nbsp;choose the top option and click <strong>&#39;Lanjutkan&#39;/&#39;Continue&#39;</strong>. Otherwise, choose the bottom option.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/coursera4.png\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">7. Below image is the screen you will see if you choose the top option. Create your password and make sure the email address is the same as the one on the announcement. Click <strong>&#39;Lanjutkan&#39;/&#39;Continue&#39;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/coursera5.png\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">8. Congratulations! You have joined the Coursera program through ICE Institute. This display is your dashboard and you can find that you&#39;re already enrolled to your chosen courses. Happy learning!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/coursera6.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">You can also join coursera program by watching this video:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe align=\"left\" frameborder=\"1\" height=\"800\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1A_bS5NFP80\" width=\"800\"></iframe></p>\r\n', 'coursera,gettingstarted,iceinstitute,ice,panduanmahasiswa', 14, 24, 2, 'post', '63d9ecaa912c8.png', '2023-02-01 12:38:02', '2023-02-06 08:51:38', 801),
('63e0fc1eea5f2', 'Guide to Getting Started on Coursera Courses - ICE Institute', 'guide-to-getting-started-on-coursera-courses-ice-institute', 'Langkah - langkah dalam memulai mata kuliah internasional coursera melalui ice institute, panduan ini berfungsi untuk para peserta', '<h1><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px\">PANDUAN MEMULAI MATA KULIAH INTERNASIONAL COURSERA - ICE INSTITUTE</span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\">A.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Memulai Mata Kuliah Internasional Coursera &ndash; ICE Institute</span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Peserta akan mendapatkan email pemberitahuan terkait info untuk memulai mata kuliah internasional Coursera &ndash; ICE Institute. Klik tombol <strong>Join Now</strong> untuk melanjutkan proses, seperti gambar 1 di bawah ini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 1. Pemberitahuan Memulai Mata Kuliah</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/C11.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Gambar 2 berisi info terkait penggunaan Coursera untuk pertama kali atau tidak, klik tombol <em><strong>Continue</strong></em> untuk melanjutkan, seperti gambar 2 di bawah ini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 2. Penggunaan Coursera Untuk Pertama Kali Atau Tidak</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc2.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Pengguna baru diminta untuk membuat <em><strong>password </strong></em>dengan alamat email yang tercantum seperti gambar 3. Pastikan membuat dan mengingat <em><strong>password </strong></em>supaya dapat masuk kembali ke dalam akun yang telah dibuat. Lalu klik tombol <em><strong>Continue</strong></em> untuk melanjutkan. Kemudian akan diberikan panduan singkat, seperti tampilan seperti gambar 4 di bawah ini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 3. Pembuatan Akun</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc3.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 4. Panduan Singkat</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc4.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Gunakan Kolom pencarian seperti di bawah ini untuk mencari mata kuliah dengan menuliskan nama mata kuliah yang sesuai dengan Daftar Pengumuman (lihat gambar 5). Contohnya Mata Kuliah <em>The Dynamic Earth: A Course for Educators dari American Museum of Natural History</em> (Lihat Gambar 6).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 5. Pencarian Mata Kuliah</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc5.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 6. Contoh Mata Kuliah</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc6.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Klik nama mata kuliah yang muncul pada tampilan seperti gambar 7, kemudian klik tombol <em>Enroll </em>untuk memulai mata kuliah.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 7. Enroll Mata Kuliah</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc7.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Jika berhasil, maka tombol enroll akan berubah menjadi <em>Go to Course</em> seperti gambar 8 di bawah ini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 8. Go to Course</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc8.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Klik tombol <em>Go to Course</em> untuk memulai mata kuliah.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Untuk mata kuliah yang lain, lakukan cara seperti di atas dan pastikan nama mata kuliah yang dipilih sesuai dengan yang didaftarkan.</span></strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Selamat belajar dan mendapatkan sertifikat!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\">B.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Masuk Kembali ke dalam Mata Kuliah</span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Mengakses mata kuliah melalui web browser dengan mengetikkan URL link<strong> <a href=\"https://icei.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\">www.icei.ac.id</a></strong> kemudian klik <strong>Masuk</strong>, seperti yang terlihat pada gambar 10 di bawah ini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 10. Mata Kuliah di ICE Institute</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc9.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Klik menu <strong>Universitas/Institusi/Lembaga</strong>, lalu cari Logo Coursera seperti gambar 11 di bawah ini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 11. Menu Tampilan Mata Kuliah</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc9.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Klik tombol <strong>Lihat </strong>yang berada di bawah logo Coursera yang akan mengarah ke halaman baru seperti gambar 12 di bawah ini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Gambar 12. Program International Course</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc10.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Silakan memasukkan <em><strong>email </strong></em>dan <em><strong>password </strong></em>seperti pada langkah<strong> tahap A.3</strong> sebelumnya.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px\">A GUIDE ON HOW TO START COURSES INTERNATIONAL COURSERA - ICE INSTITUTE</span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\">A.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Starting International Course Coursera &ndash; ICE Institute</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Participants will receive an email notification regarding an invitation to start the Coursera &ndash; ICE Institute international course, as shown below (Figure 1).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 1. Email Notification</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/C11.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Click the <strong>Join Now</strong> button to continue the process, choose user status (new or existing user), and click the Continue button (see Figure 2).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 2. New User or Existing User&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc2.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Create a password with the email address for new user as shown in Figure 3. Make sure to remember the email and password then click the Continue button to continue.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 3. Create Account</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc3.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;User will be given a brief guide. You can learn it, or skip it (see Figure 4).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 4. Brief Guide</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc4.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Use searching box to search the course (see Figure 5). For Example, The Dynamic Earth Course: A Course for Educators from the American Museum of Natural History (see figure 6).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 5. Searching Courses</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc5.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 6. Searching Example</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc6.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Click <strong>Enroll </strong>button to start the course (see figure 7).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 7. Enroll the course. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc7.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;If successful, the enroll button will change to <strong>Go to Course</strong> as shown below (Figure 8).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 8. Go To Course&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc8.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Start the course by clicking the <strong>Go to Course</strong> button.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Do the same ways for other courses and make sure the name of the selected course matched.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Happy learning!</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>B.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Re-enter the Course&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Access the course through web browser by typing the URL link <strong><a href=\"http://icei.ac.id\" target=\"_blank\">www.icei.ac.id</a></strong> then click <strong>Masuk</strong>, as shown in figure 9 below.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 9. Courses at ICE Institute</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/mkc9.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Click the <strong>Universitas/Institusi/Lembaga</strong> menu, then choose the Coursera Logo as shown below (see Figure 10).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 10. Course Menu</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc9.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Click the <strong>Lihat&nbsp;</strong>button under the Coursera logo that will be directed to a new page like the image below (see Figure 11).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Figure 11. Program International Course</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/pc10.png\" style=\"width:100%\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Enter email and password (follow <strong>step A.3</strong>).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px\">By: Musowwir Lubis and Afriani</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'icei,ice institute,indonesia cyber edcation intitute,memulai mata kuliah di ice institute', 14, 24, 2, 'post', 'default.jpg', '2023-02-06 09:09:50', '2023-03-10 12:33:37', 2154);
