('64b4c592dfb7a', 'The 23rd Cyber Education Forum (CEF)', 'the-23rd-cyber-education-forum-cef', 'ICE Institute kembali menyelenggarakan Webinar Series Cyber Education Forum (CEF) ke-23 dengan topik \"Online Learning Process: Challenges and Opportunities\"', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://info.icei.ac.id/upload/WhatsApp_Image_2023-07-17_at_10_59_01.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Halo teman - teman ICE Institute,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ICE Institute kembali menyelenggarakan Webinar Series Cyber Education Forum (CEF) ke-23&nbsp;dengan topik &quot;Online Learning Process: Challenges and Opportunities&quot; yang diselenggarakan pada</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Senin, 24 Juli 2023<br />\r\n10.00-12.00 WIB melalui Zoom.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kegiatan akan dihadiri oleh:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Prof. Paulina Pannen, M.LS. (ICE Institute)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Prof. Jintavee Khlaisang (Chulalongkorn University)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Fajar Arwadi, S.Pd., M.Sc. (Universitas Negeri Makassar)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moderator oleh Ami Hibatul Jameel, S.Pd., M.A.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pendaftaran pada link <a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/daftarCEF23\"><strong>https://link.icei.ac.id/daftarCEF2</strong></a><a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/daftarCEF23\"><strong>3</strong></a>, GRATIS!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saksikan live streaming melalui zoom: <strong><a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/CEF23rd\">https://link.icei.ac.id/CEF23</a></strong><a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/CEF23rd\"><strong>rd</strong></a><br />\r\ndan dapat disaksikan juga pada channel YouTube UTTV <a href=\"https://link.icei.ac.id/StreamingCEF\"><strong>https://link.icei.ac.id/StreamingCEF</strong></a></p>\r\n', 'webinarseries,23rdCEF,ICE,cybereducationforum', 7, 10, 2, 'delete', '64b4c592dfb7a.png', '2023-07-17 12:37:38', '2023-